snippet.title: Bunny's Favorite Pizza
snippet.description: Bunny's Favorite Pizza is an adorable dessert pizza that will be a real hit at the kid's table. It's completely easy-to-make and a fun way to cook with your kids.

snippet.title: Blended Hazelnut Frappe
snippet.description: This is a perfect slushy coffee drink to enjoy when the temperature outside starts heating up.

snippet.title: Iced Mochaccino
snippet.description: Scrumptious coffee and chocolate flavors add depth to this elegant and easy Iced Mochaccino beverage.

snippet.title: Frozen Chocolate-Covered Cappuccino Crunch Cake
snippet.description: Cappuccino Crunch Cake combines coffee ice cream, pound cake and NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Milk Chocolate Morsels for a rich and creamy frozen dessert! This dessert was created by Beth Royals of Richmond, VA.

snippet.title: One Big Cookie
snippet.description: Enjoy some family time with the kids making these memorable cookies. They'll have fun creating their own edible masterpieces.

snippet.title: Café Collections Iced Coffee
snippet.description: With the variety of Café Collections Coffee-mate flavors available, it's easy to mix up an iced coffee that can quickly become your favorite.
